His guard may have been down,

00:00:08.432 --> 00:00:10.726
but even so,
there aren't many humans

00:00:10.768 --> 00:00:13.020
who could take out a Class S hero.

00:00:14.146 --> 00:00:16.565
Indeed. The killer is probably...

00:00:17.316 --> 00:00:18.484
one of us here!

00:00:23.239 --> 00:00:24.657
But which one?

