00:00:31.622 --> 00:00:34.208
We were honored as persons
of distinguished service

00:00:34.250 --> 00:00:36.669
for saving the Earth
from alien invasions

00:00:36.710 --> 00:00:38.420
and preventing the largest disaster
in history.

