One-Punch Folk Song

00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:44.961
“There's no way |,
Speed-o-Sound Sonic,

00:11:45.003 --> 00:11:47.297
could ever sing with
a bunch of heroes!”

00:11:47.339 --> 00:11:50.175
"Stop complaining
and start singing.”

00:11:50.258 --> 00:11:53.261
"Humph, |, King,
the strongest man on earth,

00:11:53.303 --> 00:11:54.804
will sing a solo.”

00:11:54.846 --> 00:11:58.099
“That's the spirit!
We can all sing nicely together!”

00:11:58.141 --> 00:11:59.643
(Ah, that's the way,
that's the way)

00:11:59.726 --> 00:12:03.146
One attack, one kill, ONE PUNCH

00:12:03.230 --> 00:12:07.651
